📘 **BOOTSTRAP & CSS NOTES**

---

 🔹 Bootstrap Utility Classes

**Border & Text**

* `rounded-1` → small border radius
* `text-muted` → muted/lighter text
* `text-nowrap` → prevents text wrapping

---

🔹 Display (Responsive Visibility)

* `d-none` → hide element
* `d-md-block` → visible on tablet & desktop only
* `d-md-none` → visible on mobile only

**Examples:**

* `d-none d-md-block` → hidden on mobile, visible on desktop
* `d-md-none` → mobile only

---

🔹 Background Styling Example

.body {
height: 100vh;
width: 100%;
background-image: url("image/desktop-bg.png");
background-size: cover;
background-position: center;
background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

---

🔹 Font Weights

* Regular → 400
* Semi-Bold → 600

---

🔹 Layout Tip

* `g-0` → removes spacing (gutters)
  ✔ apply to `.row` or `.col`

---
